4ac3			; | APPEND ( u n --  )  Appends data u to file id on current storage bank | DONE 
4ac3			; | | e.g. 
4ac3			; | | Test CREATE      -> $01 
4ac3			; | | "A string to add to file" $01 APPEND 
4ac3			; | |  
4ac3			; | | The maximum file size currently using 32k serial EEPROMS using 64 byte blocks is 15k. 
